name: TieDye Village
description: I remember when I was doing real work college activities somewhere near my campus, Mojosongo village, Central Java. I initiated the "TieDye" workshop program which applies it to t-shirts for children aged 6 to 15 years for 1 month. they were all very enthusiastic about joining my program, one thing I remember that resonates is the sound of children cheering as if celebrating their own success from making "TieDye" t-shirts. There is so much fun in the program that their parents join in on the celebrations, occasionally snapping photos of them. I pray that the Mojosongo village that I empower will become more independent and develop so that it can return to being a prosperous, just, and prosperous archipelagic nation.
